room_title: Escape room "Wizards and Spells" by Music City Escape Room in Nashville
review: The Wizards and Spells room was great for any Harry Potter fan! We were able to complete with 2 adults and 2 kids. The wands can be a little tricky, but they coached us through it. Thought the room was entertaining and fun! We would come back!

room_title: Escape room "Wizards and Spells" by Music City Escape Room in Nashville
review: We did the Wizards and Spells room and enjoyed it! Ryan was our host and gave great instructions. The escape room was well organized, and we enjoyed the process. If you're a Harry Potter nerd, I would recommend this! Thanks again, Ryan!

room_title: Escape room "Wizards and Spells" by Music City Escape Room in Nashville
review: We had an awesome time on a bachelorette party here! We did the wizards room and broke out just in time! The host was great and gave us helpful hints when we needed them. We wished we had time to do more rooms!
